  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >God is missing. Hell is full. Someone has taken over, and now souls must earn their place to stay in hell. <strong>PLAYING GOD</strong> is an ultra fast-paced speedrunning platformer where you take control of Dunte the duck to run, jump, and dash your way through the nine circles of hell and rebel against the mysterious entity playing god. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/cabe846db2cbdbc13d8a0610839f1923.poster.avif?t=1764343973\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/cabe846db2cbdbc13d8a0610839f1923.webm?t=1764343973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/cabe846db2cbdbc13d8a0610839f1923.mp4?t=1764343973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A SKILL-BASED PLATFORMER</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tight Movement Mechanics</strong> – No abilities, no gimmicks, no frills. The game is solely focused on movement and speeding through the courses as fast as you can.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Randomness</strong> – Only your own skill stands between you and clearing the level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One-Screen</strong> – All levels are single-screen only; pure action condensed into a tight package with no bloat or fillers.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/fd6f6c77b54a237411d54d8db932b54f.poster.avif?t=1764343973\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/fd6f6c77b54a237411d54d8db932b54f.webm?t=1764343973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/fd6f6c77b54a237411d54d8db932b54f.mp4?t=1764343973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SPEEDRUNNING INFERNO</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn medals based on your clear times in each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Etch your name into the leaderboards and compete for the fastest time.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/f876b49aea92b36822ccc4c418543d22.poster.avif?t=1764343973\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/f876b49aea92b36822ccc4c418543d22.webm?t=1764343973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/f876b49aea92b36822ccc4c418543d22.mp4?t=1764343973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY GOD YOURSELF</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features a built-in level editor for you to create your own hellish courses and share with your friends.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/531da4524c5461b759f60ff07d0ab5c4.poster.avif?t=1764343973\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/531da4524c5461b759f60ff07d0ab5c4.webm?t=1764343973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/531da4524c5461b759f60ff07d0ab5c4.mp4?t=1764343973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our community Discord and discuss strategies and techniques, share your scores, get updates on the game, and hang out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/9a7414f23ccc0609bbca1fde6d6afb6d.avif?t=1764343973\" width=512 height=128 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >God is missing. Hell is full. Someone has taken over, and now souls must earn their place to stay in hell. <strong>PLAYING GOD</strong> is an ultra fast-paced speedrunning platformer where you take control of Dunte the duck to run, jump, and dash your way through the nine circles of hell and rebel against the mysterious entity playing god. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/cabe846db2cbdbc13d8a0610839f1923.poster.avif?t=1764343973\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/cabe846db2cbdbc13d8a0610839f1923.webm?t=1764343973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/cabe846db2cbdbc13d8a0610839f1923.mp4?t=1764343973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A SKILL-BASED PLATFORMER</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tight Movement Mechanics</strong> – No abilities, no gimmicks, no frills. The game is solely focused on movement and speeding through the courses as fast as you can.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Randomness</strong> – Only your own skill stands between you and clearing the level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One-Screen</strong> – All levels are single-screen only; pure action condensed into a tight package with no bloat or fillers.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165320/extras/fd6f6c77b54a237411d54d8db932b54f.poster.avif?t=1764343973\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstat